item.title: Need help in making a server
item.dc:creator: @Cres Cres
item.description:
@Cres wrote:

1;
go to c: program files: java :jdk
now at ( not in ) the jdk folder , you wil see some numbers
memorize the last 2 numbers ( usually 20 or 21 )

go to your compiler , right click and select edit.
now you should see a path.
find for JDK in that path and change the last 2 numbers in that line to whatever your jdk version is.

do this for both the client and server compiler.
